---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SectionHeader from '../components/SectionHeader.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About | TechSoft Systems"
  description="About Jonathan (John) and TechSoft Systems private AI and infrastructure practice."
>
  <section class="pt-12">
    <SectionHeader title="About" subtitle="TechSoft Systems is led by Jonathan (John), focused on private AI platforms and resilient infrastructure delivery." />

    <div class="mt-8 rounded-3xl border border-zinc-300/50 bg-white/80 p-8 dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-white/5">
      <p class="text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300">
        Jonathan (John) helps organizations build and operate secure infrastructure and private AI systems that hold up under real operational pressure.
        The work spans architecture design, migration programs, reliability engineering, and team enablement with an emphasis on practical outcomes.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300">
        Core focus areas include containerized workloads, GPU-backed inference stacks, observability, and compliance-aware delivery.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
